Western magic obelisk
To lessen the danger to the Khadaganian soldiers of a manhunt in Death Canyon, a number of magic obelisks have been placed at different points in the canyon. Many kinds of useful spells will be cast on anyone who uses them.
#subobj  1
Find the Western Obelisk
This magic Obelisk is located near the western wall of the Canyon.
#subobj  2
Use the Obelisk
It never occurred to the people who put the magic Obelisks in place that they can be used, not only by the soldiers, but by the victims as well!
